examples.en: He faced a whole array of problems.

examples.en: He faced the reporters with his wife at his side.
examples.ru: Он пошел на встречу с репортёрами в сопровождении жены.

examples.en: He faced the terrible consequences of his mistakes.

examples.en: The problems she faced were a real test of character.

examples.en: Jackson faced Smith in the boxing ring.

examples.en: Her window faced the backs of the houses.

examples.en: We faced a harmonious group of buildings.

examples.en: They faced a grave decision in a time of crisis.
examples.ru: Им предстояло принять серьёзное решение в кризисный момент.

examples.ru: Он развернул их в сторону двери, как бы выпроваживая.

examples.en: Smith faced total public disgrace after the incident.

examples.en: The opponents faced each other across the chessboard.
